properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 12 at 11:57AM EST until January 12 at 7:00PM EST by NWS Mount Holly NJ
properties.description:
* WHAT...West winds 10 to 20 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas
5 to 8 feet.

* WHERE...The Atlantic coastal waters adjacent to New Jersey and
Delaware. Delaware Bay Waters south of East Point NJ to
Slaughter Beach DE.

* WHEN...Until 7 PM EST this evening.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 PM EST THIS EVENING... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
